The paper discusses a perception system for long-term robot manipulation, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The system involves object and scene perception, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of symbolic and numeric representations, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
